-- 2011-02-03T13:36:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-03/j-c-penney-raises-fourth-quarter-forecast-exceeding-analysts-estimates.html
J.C. Penney raised its fourth-quarter
earnings forecast to $1.06 to $1.09 a share, up from a previous
prediction of as much as $1 a share.  Analysts project 97 cents, according to the average of
estimates compiled by Bloomberg.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
